    <content lang="en">
      <city>Bern</city>
      <title>SERI News novembre 2014</title>
      <lead>Information from the State Secretariat for Education, Research and Innovation SERI</lead>
      <text link="no">&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SERI comes together at a single site&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;SERI takes up residence at Einsteinstrasse 2 in Bern &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Federal Commission for Scholarships for Foreign Students&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Life-changing scholarships &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Scholarships for the College of Europe and the European University Institute&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;A long tradition of building bridges in Europe &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Examinations for the Federal PET Diploma and Advanced Federal PET Diploma&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Established pathway enabling professionals to obtain tertiary-level qualifications &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Apprenticeship market barometer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Stabile situation on the apprenticeship market &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pilot project&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Validation of prior learning for VET and PET professionals &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Making VET and PET qualifications clearer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;NQF VPET successfully launched &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Subsidies for construction of university buildings&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Maison de la Paix as a location for education, research and promotion of peace &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;European research institutions&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;50 years of successful European cooperation in molecular biology &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Active and Assisted Living (AAL) Forum 2014 in Bucharest&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Awards given to Swiss researchers &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Annual Meeting of ERI Foreign Network&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Lively exchange of experiences and a source of inspiration&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</text>
      <contact>medien@sbfi.admin.ch</contact>
